<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9240</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17391</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森一整天都在玩儿电子游戏。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17391</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22047</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他忙着要把游戏升级到第五级。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22047</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28278</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，他一边走向儿童中心，一边打龙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28278</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31625</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他正在打第四级的最后一战……</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31625</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34860</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>咚！他撞到了尼娜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34860</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40928</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“走路时小心点！” 尼娜大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40928</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46238</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起，尼娜，我正要……” 贾森说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46238</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51866</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把电子游戏收起来吧。” 雪莉老师提醒贾森，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53815</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57595</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天的活动需要一本英文词典！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57595</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63596</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比抱怨，“词典？为什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63596</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66790</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师拿起一张厚纸，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66790</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69995</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>上面写着她的英文名字。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69995</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要做英文名字诗书签。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76709</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森把游戏机放进背包。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76709</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80107</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么是英文名字诗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80107</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是用你英文名里的字母写的诗。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86082</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师解释说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86082</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89915</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“比如说，我的英文名叫Marie。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89915</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94008</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第一行就是第一个字母开头，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94008</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97704</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二行是第二个字母开头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97704</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103557</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每一行都要写出你的特点。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103557</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106657</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“Magical（有魔法的）。” 伊坦说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106658</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110280</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么，伊坦？” 雪莉老师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110280</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113767</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您的诗的第一行。” 他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113767</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116423</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“因为您像有魔法一样，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116423</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120020</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>让各种事情变得有趣。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120020</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124233</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么要用英文词典？” 尼娜问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124233</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127865</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “你想不出来的时候，可以查词典。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127865</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133511</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师给大家发了一张空白的书签，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133511</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139304</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把名字诗写在这上面，就可以用它作书签了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139304</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144643</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森在纸上写下自己的英文名字Jason。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144643</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147615</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>字母J不容易作诗。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147613</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150178</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“Jolly（欢乐的）？” 他想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150179</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152497</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“感觉像圣诞老人。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152497</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154750</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接下来是字母A。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154750</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157833</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157833</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160741</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他写诗实在很糟糕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160741</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167295</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“Awful（糟糕）！英文的‘糟糕’是A开头的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167309</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173230</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> 他看着字母S，打了个哈欠。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173231</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177667</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“Sleepy（困的）！” 他想。这个比较简单。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177667</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179907</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后是字母O。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179907</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184866</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森打开字典看字母O的第一页。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184866</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187912</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大部分词他都不知道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187913</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192201</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看了所有字母O开头的单词。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192201</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197340</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他觉得“Odd（奇怪的）” 是唯一一个可以用的单词。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200031</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都写好后，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199962</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204195</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师让伊坦读一读他的诗。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204196</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207190</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的英文名是Ethan，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207190</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208970</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>Excellent surfer（很棒的冲浪手）、</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208970</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210571</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>Totally cool（非常酷）、</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210571</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>Helpful（会帮助人）、</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213732</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>Adventurous（爱冒险的）、</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213732</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216147</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>New（新的）。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216147</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219708</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“因为我是新同学。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219708</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222394</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>下一个是贾森。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222394</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223372</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“Jumpy（紧张的）、</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223372</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224483</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>Awful（糟糕的）、</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224483</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225573</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>Sleepy（困的）、</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225573</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226409</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>Odd（奇怪的）、</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226409</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>Nut（怪人）。” 他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232192</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怪人？” 莉琪不太理解。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232192</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239174</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我看到‘nut’这个单词的意思是奇怪或者很蠢的人。” 他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239174</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244541</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“贾森，这些说的是你吗？” 雪莉老师问,</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244542</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250567</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这些也可以，但是我可以想到更好的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250567</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对，比如说J可以是 ‘Jigsaw puzzle wizard (七巧板天才)’！” 波比说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257116</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260171</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你玩儿七巧板很厉害。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260171</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264110</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“ ‘A’可以是 ‘awesome’（很棒的）。” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264110</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268595</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“ ‘S’可以是 ‘super’（超级的）。” 莉琪补充说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268595</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270372</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“或者 ‘sweet’（亲切的）。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270372</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272415</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“ ‘O’可以是 ‘only’（唯一的）。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272415</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278822</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为你是唯一一个把游戏打到第四级的人！” 伊坦说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278822</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283701</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森笑了，“你们都好厉害！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283701</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他写下新诗。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290199</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但留着‘怪人’吧。” 波比笑着说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290199</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294055</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“因为有时你确实很奇怪。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>